Why VueGL ❓ Vue.js render into DOM and three.js renders into Canvas.

What VueGL ❓  VueGL components render data to WebGL canvas declaretively and dynamically.

How to install ❓ npm i vue three vue-gl

Main contains what ❓
    1.VglRenderer 👉  example:<vgl-renderer class="getting-started"></vgl-renderer>   👉initializes a canvas.
    
How to Draw 3D object on canvas ❓ 
    need what ❓ 
        1.  define a scene and a camera in VglRenderer’s default slot.
        scene 决定 图形.
        camera 决定 位置.